C)pair work: steal his look: point out items your partner has and ask him how much the cost:
4)look at the pictures and answer where the locations are: doko, koko, soko, asoko
  1)toire wa doko desu ka? koko desu 2)toshokan wa doko desu ka? asoko desu 3)kutsu wa doko desu ka? soko desu 4)yasai wa doko desu ka? asoko desu
  5)menyuu wa doko desu ka? koko desu 6)eego no hon wa doko desu ka? koko desu
5)Pair work: point at each object and ask partner whose it is: kore wa dare no noun desu ka?
